column5: Nice, those guy catch some massive fish on those lakes.

Yeah it's fishing news, but people always post on the main forum about how much the leafs suck and nobody says anything about that so I don't see a problem with somebody posting the results of a Fishing tournament on the main discussion page of this wonderful fishing forum!  Good for G - he deserves it, and now he can swing for the fences the rest of the season because he's in the classic no matter what!  Cheers, Ryan
